并需要试验空间与呼吸独立；B方承载内在根基与情感基座，用私密方式守护安全感，也需要稳定、被理解的家与归属。因此小题容易升级为角力，却也逼迫彼此成长。只要先理解对方诉求再辩驳，把冲突当成调校机制，就能持续磨合能炼出更有韧性的关系结构。"},{"target":"A盘海王星 合相 B盘下降","description":"A的海王星与B的下降形成合相，能量高度重叠，牵引力强烈，仿佛彼此的磁场瞬间对准。A方代表梦想共情与灵性融合，以想象力与无条件包容渗透氛围，并需要浪漫愿景落地而不迷失；B方承载关系模式与伙伴镜像，透过互动映照自我，也需要平衡彼此需求与界线。因此默契来得快，也会加速显露彼此的优点与控制欲。只要留些独处与界线，练习轮流主导与倾听，就能让集中火力沉淀为携手突破的核心动力。"},{"target":"A盘冥王星 六分相 B盘下降","description":"A的冥王星与B的下降形成六合，彼此自然互补，容易找到合作切点和共同节奏。A方代表深度洞察与转化力量，以极致专注直指灵魂核心，并需要诚实交付权力并拥抱新生；B方承载关系模式与伙伴镜像，透过互动映照自我，也需要平衡彼此需求与界线。因此互动轻松有建设性，但若缺乏推动力也会停在舒适区。只要善用灵感立即落地，把灵气转成共同项目，就能持续产出1+1>2的成果并加深信任。"}]},"chart_svg":{"a_in_b":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\"?>\n        <svg width=\"720\" height=\"720\"\n             shape-rendering=\"geometricPrecision\"\n             viewBox=\"0 0 720 720\"\n             xmlns=\"http:\/\/www.w3.org\/2000\/svg\"\n             class=\"astrology-chart\"\n             data-chart-type=\"synastry\"\n             data-chart-engine=\"yuanfenju-modern-svg\"\n             data-chart-version=\"1.0\"\n             data-api-version=\"1.0\"\n             data-layout-version=\"1.3\"\n             data-style-contract=\"css-variables-v1\">\n            <defs>\n                <style type=\"text\/css\">\n                    <![CDATA[\n                    :root {\n                        --chart-text-color: currentColor;\n                        --chart-font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\n\n                        --chart-ring-stroke: currentColor;\n\n                        --color-person-a: #000;\n                        --color-person-b: #555;\n\n                        --chart-aspect-hard-color: #d00;\n                        --chart-aspect-soft-color: #0a0;\n                        --chart-aspect-minor-color: #0b0;\n                        --chart-aspect-square-color: #00a;\n                        --chart-aspect-quincunx-color: #fa0;\n                        --chart-retrograde-color: red;\n                        --chart-connector-stroke-a: var(--color-person-a);\n                        --chart-connector-stroke-b: var(--color-person-b);\n\n                        \/* 新增显式声明（文档要求） *\/\n                        --chart-house-axis-width: 2.5;\n                        --chart-planet-hit-area-radius: 18;\n                    }\n\n                    \/* 其余样式保持不变 *\/\n                    .ring, .house-cusp-line, .aspect, .planet-connector, .center-cross path {\n                        fill: none;\n                        stroke: var(--chart-ring-stroke);\n                        vector-effect: non-scaling-stroke;\n                        stroke-linecap: butt;\n                    }\n\n                    .ring-outer { stroke-width: var(--chart-ring-outer-width, 3); }\n                    .ring-zodiac-inner { stroke-width: var(--chart-ring-zodiac-inner-width, 2); fill: none; }\n                    .ring-house-inner { stroke-width: var(--chart-ring-house-inner-width, 1.2); opacity: var(--chart-house-inner-opacity, 0.5); }\n                    .ring-planet-b-outer { stroke-width: var(--chart-ring-planet-b-width, 1.4); opacity: var(--chart-planet-b-ring-opacity, 0.35); }\n                    .ring-planet-b-inner { stroke-width: var(--chart-ring-planet-b-width, 1.4); opacity: var(--chart-planet-b-ring-opacity, 0.35); }\n                    .ring-planet-a-outer { stroke-width: var(--chart-ring-planet-a-width, 1.4); opacity: var(--chart-planet-a-ring-opacity, 0.35); }\n                    .ring-planet-a-inner { stroke-width: var(--chart-ring-planet-a-width, 1.4); opacity: var(--chart-planet-a-ring-opacity, 0.35); }\n                    .ring-aspect { stroke-width: var(--chart-ring-aspect-width, 1.2); opacity: var(--chart-aspect-ring-opacity, 0.25); }\n\n                    .house-cusp-line { stroke-width: var(--chart-house-cusp-width, 1.2); opacity: var(--chart-house-cusp-opacity, 0.65); }\n                    .house-cusp-line.axis { stroke-width: var(--chart-house-axis-width, 2.5); opacity: var(--chart-house-axis-opacity, 0.9); }\n\n                    .aspect { opacity: var(--chart-aspect-opacity, 0.45); }\n\n                    .aspect-conjunction, .aspect-opposition {\n                        stroke: var(--chart-aspect-hard-color);\n                        stroke-width: var(--chart-aspect-hard-width, 2.5);\n                        stroke-dasharray: var(--chart-aspect-hard-dash, 5,3);\n                    }\n                    .aspect-semisextile, .aspect-quincunx {\n                        stroke: var(--chart-aspect-minor-color);\n                        stroke-width: var(--chart-aspect-minor-width, 1.2);\n                        stroke-dasharray: var(--chart-aspect-minor-dash, 1,5);\n                    }\n                    .aspect-sextile, .aspect-trine {\n                        stroke: var(--chart-aspect-soft-color);\n                        stroke-width: var(--chart-aspect-soft-width, 1.5);\n                        stroke-dasharray: var(--chart-aspect-soft-dash, 2,4);\n                    }\n                    .aspect-square {\n                        stroke: var(--chart-aspect-square-color);\n                        stroke-width: var(--chart-aspect-square-width, 2);\n                        stroke-dasharray: var(--chart-aspect-square-dash, 3,3);\n                    }\n\n                    text {\n                        fill: var(--chart-text-color);\n                        font-family: var(--chart-font-family);\n                    }\n\n                    .planet-person-a text { fill: var(--color-person-a); }\n                    .planet-person-b text { fill: var(--color-person-b); }\n\n                    .planet-person-a .planet-connector { stroke: var(--chart-connector-stroke-a); }\n                    .planet-person-b .planet-connector { stroke: var(--chart-connector-stroke-b); }\n\n                    .house-number { font-size: var(--chart-house-number-size, 16px); }\n                    .zodiac-sign { font-size: var(--chart-zodiac-sign-size, 28px); font-weight: bold; }\n                    .planet-symbol { font-size: var(--chart-planet-symbol-size, 18px); opacity: var(--chart-planet-symbol-opacity, 0.85); }\n                    .planet-position { font-size: var(--chart-planet-position-size, 10px); opacity: var(--chart-planet-position-opacity, 0.75); }\n                    .planet-sign-symbol { font-size: var(--chart-planet-sign-symbol-size, 20px); font-weight: bold; }\n                    .retrograde-indicator { font-size: var(--chart-retrograde-size, 12px); fill: var(--chart-retrograde-color); }\n\n                    .planet-connector {\n                        stroke-width: var(--chart-connector-width, 0.8);\n                        opacity: var(--chart-connector-opacity, 0.25);\n                    }\n\n                    .planet-hit-area { fill: none; opacity: 0; cursor: pointer; }\n                    ]]>\n                <\/style>\n            <\/defs>\n\n            <g class=\"chart\"\n               data-layout-token=\"chart-root\"\n               data-outer-radius=\"310\"\n               data-zodiac-outer-radius=\"310\"\n               data-zodiac-inner-radius=\"260\"\n               data-house-outer-radius=\"260\"\n               data-house-inner-radius=\"230\"\n               data-planet-outer-radius-b=\"230\"\n               data-planet-inner-radius-b=\"195\"\n               data-planet-outer-radius-a=\"195\"\n               data-planet-inner-radius-a=\"160\"\n               data-aspect-radius=\"140\"\n               data-planet-stack-spacing=\"12\"\n               data-planet-label-horizontal-offset=\"20\"\n               data-planet-stack-angle=\"5\"\n               data-planet-label-line-spacing=\"20\"\n               data-planet-hit-area-radius=\"18\"\n               data-aspect-scope=\"inter\">\n                <!-- ====================== 背景结构层 ====================== -->\n                <!-- 负责绘制所有基础圆环与定位辅助线，不包含占星数据 -->\n                <g class=\"chart-layer\" data-layer=\"background\">\n                    <!-- 星盘整体最外边界 -->\n